## Common Mistakes to Avoid

**Underestimating Setup Costs**

Most manufacturers underestimate by 20-30%. Build in buffer.

**Draining All Working Capital**

Keep 6 months of operating expenses in reserve. Production delays happen.

**Buying Used Without Inspection**

Used equipment can save 30-50%, but get it inspected. Repair costs can wipe out savings.

**Ignoring Lead Times**

Some machinery takes 3-6 months to deliver from overseas. Factor this into your financing and production timeline.

**Forgetting Ongoing Costs**

Equipment financing covers the purchase. You still need budget for:
- Maintenance contracts
- Spare parts inventory
- Operator training
- Insurance

## Alternative Options

If traditional financing doesn't work, consider:

**Hire Purchase**

Pay over time and own the equipment at the end. Similar to a loan but structured differently for tax purposes.

**Operating Lease**

Rent equipment with option to buy later. Lower monthly payments but you don't own it during the lease.

**Vendor Financing**

Some equipment suppliers offer in-house financing, especially for expensive machinery (RM500k+).

**Government Grants**

Check MIDA and SME Corp for manufacturing incentives. These can reduce your capital needs by 10-30%.

## Frequently Asked Questions

**Can I get a loan for a brand-new factory with no revenue?**

Yes, if you have:
- Strong business plan
- Experienced management team
- Sufficient down payment (20-30%)
- Personal financial strength
- Clear route to revenue

We've financed many first-time factory setups.

**How long does approval take?**

With complete documentation: 3-5 working days for principle approval, 2-3 weeks to disbursement.

**What if I need more later?**

Most lenders allow top-up financing once you've proven good payment history (6-12 months).

**Can I finance used equipment?**

Yes, up to 10 years old typically. Loan tenure will be shorter (3-5 years max).

**Do I need to own the factory building?**

No. Most manufacturers lease. The equipment serves as collateral, not the building.

